<div class="container">


  <header class="container ">
    <h1 id="Regheader">FIGHT WORLD HUNGER!</h1>
  </header>


  <div class=" jumbotron ">
    <div class="problem">
      <h2>Why is world hunger a problem?</h2>
       <h5>Millions of people around the world are simply too poor to be able to buy food. They also lack the resources to grow their own food, such as arable land and the means to harvest, process, and store food.</h5>
       <a href="#register-form"><button id= "take-action-button"type="button">Sign Up!</button></a>

    </div>

 </div>

 <div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm text-white">
      <h2>EDUCATION</h2>
      <img class="landing-pg-images" id='children-classroom' src="children-classroom.jpg" alt="children in classroom">
      <p class="description">The effects of hunger on education are startling. Chronic hunger can prevent students from making the most of a formal education, no matter how hard they try to ignore its effects. The sad truth is that hunger can have physical and psychological effects on young people that make learning substantially difficult.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm text-white">
      <h2>JOBS</h2>
      <img class="landing-pg-images" id="jobless-man" src="jobless.jpg" alt="homeless man">
      <p class="description">Among the factors that often contribute to poverty are unemployment and underemployment. Put simply, many people live in poverty because they are unable to find a job </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm text-white">
      <h2>LAND</h2>
      <img class="landing-pg-images " id= 'plant-image'src="plant.jpg" alt="plant image">
      <p class="description">Land is fundamental to the
lives of poor rural people. It is
a source of food, shelter,
income and social identity.
Secure access to land
reduces vulnerability to
hunger and poverty. But for
many of the world’s poor
rural people in developing
countries, access is becoming
more tenuous than ever.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-sm text-white">
     <h2>FOOD</h2>
     <img class ="landing-pg-images"id='african-children-image' src="african-children.jpg" alt="African children image">
     <p class="description">The world produces enough food for everyone to live a healthy, productive life. The challenge is not a lack of food, it’s making food consistently available to everyone who needs it.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="col-sm text-white">
     <h2>INVESTMENT</h2>
     <img id="coins" class="landing-pg-images"src="coins.jpg" alt="coins">
     <p class="description">Foreign direct investment is a key ingredient of successful economic growth and development in developing countries</p>

   </div>

 </div>
</div>



